  <h2>postgresql gem on Leopard stock gem system</h2>
  <p class="auth">Posted by kev
  <span class="typo_date" title="Sun, 23 Dec 2007 01:24:00 GMT">Sun, 23 Dec 2007 01:24:00 GMT</span></p>
  <div id="adsense">
  <script type="text/javascript"><!--
